        The k-means algorithm, also known as Lloyd's algorithm. The algorithm uses early stopping when the new clusters error/current cluster error >= errorLimit.
        Parameters:
        clusters - the number of clusters to use
        maxIterations - the maximum number of iterations the algorithm recalculates centers
